entry.title: Invocation of the Alien Enemies Act
entry.content: This is the full text of the executive order titled 'Invocation of the Alien Enemies Act Regarding the Invasion of The United States by Tren De Aragua' which authorized the deportation of illegal aliens on March 15th, 2025.
